<TITLE>If you're happy, you'll look good: Daisy Shah</TITLE>
<TEXT>Fashion to me is 
Being comfortable in whatever you wear. 
 
5 essentials of a woman's wardrobe  
A nice pair of denims, a racerback tee, LBD, an ethnic ensemble and a decent formal shirt. 
 
 Three things I never leave home without  
My phone, sunglasses, and lip balm. 
 
 My ideal outfits for 
 -A fun party 
 A nice short dress with a pair of sassy sneakers or flats. 
 -A formal work setting  
A well-fitting formal pants with a shirt. 
 -A casual day out with friends 
 A long and flowy spaghetti dress. 
 -A hot date  
An evening gown. 
 
 My shopping strategy is  
Very quick and simple. I go shopping only when I know what I need to buy and from where. I am a smart shopper. 
 
A valuable beauty tip  
Drink water, be grateful and be happy. If you are happy, you're bound to look good. 
 
My favourite style trick 
 Casual denims with a ganji and sneakers. 
 
 A fashion trend I can't stand 
 Crop-top with a not-so-flat tummy. 
 
 Essential pairs of shoes for women 
 A pair of black, nude and gold heels each. 
 
 My ultimate fashion destinations 
 London and Dubai. 
 
 The most stylish person in showbiz  
Sonam Kapoor. She is creative and experimental. 
 
 STYLE SPEAK 
 A word for you: Fuss-free 
 As a person, I'm: Straightforward 
 Style mantra: i Keep it minimalistic 
 What makes me feel sexy: Being happy 
 My favourite perfume: Olympea by Paco Rabanne 
 Favourite colour: Black 
 My fashion icon: Eva Longoria for the way she dresses. I like Selena Gomez too.</TEXT>
